exceptions.tactic: apply diagram_comp with (X:=X) (Y:=Y) (Z:=Y) (X':=X) (Y':=Y) (RX:=TX) (RY:=R) (R:=TY) (RY':=TY')(S:=comp (star S) R) (S':=comp (star S) R').
exceptions.exn: In environment X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) Hpwf := plus_wf Hwf : well_founded (trans (plus S)) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') The term "R" has type "X -> Y -> Prop" while it is expected to have type "Y -> Y -> Prop" (cannot unify "Y" and "X").

In environment X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) Hpwf := plus_wf Hwf : well_founded (trans (plus S)) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') Unable to unify "diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R)" with "diagram (comp (star TX) TX') (comp (star S) R) (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R')".

In environment X : Set S, TX : relation X HS : diagram TX S (star TX) (plus S) Hwf : well_founded (trans S) Hpwf := plus_wf Hwf : well_founded (trans (plus S)) TX' : relation X HS' : diagram TX' S (comp (star TX) TX') (plus S) Y : Type R, R' : relation2 X Y TY, TY' : relation Y HR : diagram TX R (star TY) (comp (star S) R) HR' : diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R') Unable to unify "diagram TX' R (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R')" with "diagram (comp (star TX) TX') (comp (star S) R) (comp (star TY) TY') (comp (star S) R')".

original: apply diagram_comp with (X:=X) (Y:=Y) (Z:=Y) (X':=X) (Y':=Y) (RX:=TX) (RY:=R) (R:=TY) (RY':=TY')(S:=comp (star S) R) (S':=comp (star S) R'). apply HR. apply HR'.
